@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Sequence Diagram: Tourist Submitting Itinerary and Receiving Bids

actor Tourist
participant System
participant Driver

Tourist -> System: Login
System --> Tourist: Authenticated
Tourist -> System: Create Itinerary (Destinations, Dates, Stays)
System --> Tourist: Itinerary Created, Estimated Distance/Duration
Tourist -> System: Submit for Bids
System --> Driver: Notify Available Itinerary
Driver -> System: View Itinerary Details
Driver -> System: Submit Bid (Price, Vehicle Details)
System --> Tourist: Notify New Bid
Tourist -> System: View/Compare Bids
Tourist -> System: Select Bid/Driver
System --> Driver: Notify Bid Accepted
Driver -> System: Accept Trip
System --> Tourist: Trip Accepted, Contact Revealed
Tourist -> Driver: Communicate via Messaging
@enduml
